WEBVTT

01:52.350 --> 01:57.539
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.509 --> 02:01.940
[Episode 16]

02:07.120 --> 02:09.750
A banquet for all exam candidates
is held tonight at Huan'e House.

02:09.750 --> 02:10.590
Is that true?

02:10.590 --> 02:11.470
Hurry up.

02:11.470 --> 02:13.360
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

02:19.280 --> 02:22.360
For ten years you've honed your blade,

02:22.360 --> 02:25.710
Your budding bloom's scent
lingers soft and mild.

02:25.710 --> 02:29.120
May all of you pass the selection exam

02:29.120 --> 02:31.120
And have your names inscribed
on the golden roll!

02:31.120 --> 02:34.280
Great.

02:34.280 --> 02:37.960
Come on, cheers.

02:37.960 --> 02:39.840
-Drink up.
-Drink up.

02:39.840 --> 02:41.630
Come on, another round.

02:44.360 --> 02:45.760
Hope we all make the list!

02:46.680 --> 02:48.310
Another round, brother!

02:48.310 --> 02:49.710
Why aren't you drinking?

02:50.000 --> 02:50.960
I can't hold my liquor.

02:50.960 --> 02:52.840
-I can't...
-C'mon, drink!

02:52.840 --> 02:54.000
Everyone, tonight,

02:54.000 --> 02:56.000
we eat, drink and enjoy!

02:56.000 --> 02:58.750
Okay, come on.

03:07.080 --> 03:07.560
Come on.

03:11.140 --> 03:12.740
I truly can't drink any more.

03:18.410 --> 03:19.440
This one's mine.

03:20.130 --> 03:21.060
Guardian Corps!

03:28.380 --> 03:29.710
Hurry upstairs! Hurry!

03:31.360 --> 03:32.560
Everyone, move fast!

03:37.280 --> 03:38.150
Move!

03:38.840 --> 03:39.630
Hurry!

03:41.079 --> 03:42.120
Young healer!

03:46.410 --> 03:48.130
Are you okay, Tian Xing?

03:49.170 --> 03:50.360
Tian Xing!

03:50.380 --> 03:51.220
It's Tian Yue.

03:52.310 --> 03:53.200
Tian Yue.

04:03.830 --> 04:04.740
Let's go.

04:35.600 --> 04:36.880
Get up, quick.

04:37.000 --> 04:38.200
Go upstairs and hide.

05:02.660 --> 05:03.650
I never stop you taking jobs

05:03.650 --> 05:05.910
to earn money regarding the Exam Tokens.

05:05.960 --> 05:07.030
But not a single hair

05:07.030 --> 05:09.360
on the woman in the portrait
can be harmed.

05:09.800 --> 05:12.530
If even one strand of her hair falls
to the ground,

05:12.670 --> 05:14.000
bring me your heads.

05:14.360 --> 05:15.090
Yes, sir.

05:25.760 --> 05:26.640
I...

05:28.820 --> 05:30.210
Hold still.

05:31.230 --> 05:32.070
The portrait.

05:33.810 --> 05:34.810
The portrait.

05:49.150 --> 05:52.000
[Pine Wind for Ten Miles]

06:01.950 --> 06:03.390
Shadow Slay League.

06:19.080 --> 06:19.960
Gao Ran.

06:19.980 --> 06:22.240
I heard you were at Huan'e House tonight.

06:40.770 --> 06:43.170
♪ Wind sheds rain like tears ♪

06:43.200 --> 06:44.750
♪ Over the whole town ♪

06:44.770 --> 06:47.430
♪ At the second our gazes meet ♪

06:47.450 --> 06:51.010
♪ Past memories roar one louder beat ♪

06:53.450 --> 06:54.650
Let me see your wound.

06:54.820 --> 06:55.940
No need.

06:56.030 --> 06:57.300
A young lady

06:57.430 --> 06:58.390
sneaking into a man's chamber at midnight

06:58.390 --> 07:00.000
will ruin your reputation.

07:01.560 --> 07:02.390
You...

07:04.310 --> 07:05.390
Let me check it.

07:12.440 --> 07:15.140
♪ Wind sheds rain like tears ♪

07:12.700 --> 07:13.700
It's...

07:14.750 --> 07:16.000
Nasty cut.

07:15.160 --> 07:16.380
♪ Over the whole town ♪

07:16.400 --> 07:18.900
♪ At the second our gazes meet ♪

07:19.050 --> 07:22.620
♪ Past memories roar one louder beat ♪

07:23.950 --> 07:25.240
Half an inch deep into the flesh.

07:25.240 --> 07:26.850
Luckily no bones are hurt,

07:25.360 --> 07:27.840
♪ Perhaps hearts long to seek ♪

07:26.920 --> 07:29.160
but wash it with clean water

07:27.860 --> 07:29.220
♪ Etch within our fingertips ♪

07:29.160 --> 07:30.750
to avoid infection.

07:29.250 --> 07:32.140
♪ Hear crisp footsteps echo clear ♪

07:30.750 --> 07:31.390
No need.

07:31.390 --> 07:32.560
I'll tend to it myself.

07:32.159 --> 07:35.640
♪ Strike out on a fearless
dream's frontier ♪

07:34.159 --> 07:35.760
Can you even see well enough?

07:36.040 --> 07:37.480
I don't like others touching me.

07:37.050 --> 07:40.390
♪ Though fleeting years rush
without delay ♪

07:39.120 --> 07:40.320
You'll get used to it.

07:40.450 --> 07:43.470
♪ A wisp of softness tints
your brow each day ♪

07:40.800 --> 07:42.000
I won't.

07:43.500 --> 07:45.500
♪ Walk side by side with moon and sun ♪

07:44.159 --> 07:45.240
You have to.

07:45.520 --> 07:48.640
♪ When all is said and all is done ♪

07:48.659 --> 07:50.659
♪ We'll ride upstream and downs ♪

07:50.690 --> 07:53.120
♪ When deep love dwells within our eyes ♪

07:53.360 --> 07:56.380
♪ Our burning longing never dies ♪

07:56.510 --> 08:01.310
♪ Wander together through wind and frost ♪

08:01.340 --> 08:03.340
♪ Every dark night fades at last ♪

08:03.360 --> 08:05.890
♪ When fate resides within our sight ♪

08:06.000 --> 08:10.680
♪ Gazing toward each
other's distant light ♪

08:10.780 --> 08:14.210
♪ Why would heaven and earth seek
to be with you to save us ♪

08:14.230 --> 08:16.390
♪ Don't let the sun down ♪

08:28.180 --> 08:30.530
♪ Wind sheds rain like tears ♪

08:30.570 --> 08:32.070
♪ Over the whole town ♪

08:32.090 --> 08:34.640
♪ At the second our gazes meet ♪

08:34.919 --> 08:38.159
♪ Past memories roar one louder beat ♪

08:41.030 --> 08:43.030
♪ Perhaps hearts long to seek ♪

08:43.200 --> 08:44.710
♪ Etch within our fingertips ♪

08:44.740 --> 08:47.390
♪ Hear crisp footsteps echo clear ♪

08:47.480 --> 08:51.140
♪ Strike out on a fearless
dream's frontier ♪

08:52.520 --> 08:55.730
♪ Though fleeting years rush
without delay ♪

08:55.840 --> 08:58.890
♪ A wisp of softness tints
your brow each day ♪

08:58.910 --> 09:01.240
♪ Walk side by side with moon and sun ♪

08:59.750 --> 09:00.750
Alright then.

09:01.150 --> 09:03.080
Damn Shadow Slay League.

09:01.260 --> 09:04.640
♪ When all is said and all is done ♪

09:03.080 --> 09:05.150
Thank goodness they didn't scar your face.

09:05.150 --> 09:05.900
Otherwise,

09:05.930 --> 09:08.130
I'd hunt them to the ends of the earth.

09:08.150 --> 09:09.020
Miss Wei,

09:09.860 --> 09:11.860
isn’t judging people by their looks

09:12.080 --> 09:13.320
rather biased?

09:13.940 --> 09:14.980
If not looks,

09:15.010 --> 09:15.890
then what?

09:19.390 --> 09:20.290
Some people

09:20.790 --> 09:21.830
look noble

09:23.230 --> 09:25.510
yet live to slaughter;

09:27.000 --> 09:29.150
Some soft and pretty

09:29.630 --> 09:31.270
yet have hearts of vipers;

09:31.270 --> 09:32.140
But some

09:32.510 --> 09:33.700
plain-looking

09:33.900 --> 09:35.100
yet loyal to the bone.

09:35.720 --> 09:36.960
Many wear

09:36.980 --> 09:38.270
fine appearances

09:38.960 --> 09:40.160
hiding rotten souls.

09:43.130 --> 09:44.210
Hearts can shift,

09:44.410 --> 09:45.330
but looks

09:45.360 --> 09:46.290
are born to stay.

09:46.460 --> 09:47.390
You’re born one way,

09:47.390 --> 09:48.720
and you grow up that way.

09:49.880 --> 09:51.880
I’ll always prefer handsome faces.

09:56.280 --> 09:57.270
Shallow.

09:58.360 --> 09:59.620
Can good-looking folk

09:59.700 --> 10:01.150
not turn to banditry?

10:02.200 --> 10:03.550
Someone with your face

10:03.550 --> 10:04.410
could never be

10:04.630 --> 10:05.660
truly wicked.

10:09.150 --> 10:10.480
Do you truly know me?

10:15.750 --> 10:16.790
I don't,

10:18.310 --> 10:19.430
but

10:20.100 --> 10:21.310
I can feel something.

10:58.300 --> 10:59.460
Miss Wei,

10:59.490 --> 11:00.900
the hour grows late.

11:01.270 --> 11:02.470
I have official duties to attend to.

11:02.470 --> 11:03.970
Farewell.

11:08.560 --> 11:10.040
This is your room.

11:54.170 --> 11:55.300
What happened here?

11:56.870 --> 11:57.530
Hold still.

11:58.260 --> 11:58.880
I got this.

11:59.110 --> 12:00.370
I... Your Excellency.

12:01.150 --> 12:01.720
Your Excellency.

12:01.720 --> 12:02.650
Are you wounded?

12:02.770 --> 12:03.740
What happened?

12:04.560 --> 12:05.560
I'm unharmed,

12:05.590 --> 12:07.190
Your Excellency, rest easy.

12:08.560 --> 12:10.220
This was your so-called plan?

12:10.600 --> 12:12.530
Why didn't you warn me beforehand?

12:13.090 --> 12:14.680
I couldn't

12:14.710 --> 12:17.370
drag Your Excellency into danger
alongside me.

12:17.790 --> 12:19.920
But you must not risk yourself either.

12:20.840 --> 12:21.480
No.

12:22.010 --> 12:23.490
This place is no longer safe.

12:23.490 --> 12:25.150
Let me escort you back at once.

12:25.610 --> 12:27.470
I cannot leave, Your Excellency.

12:27.670 --> 12:28.750
I can't leave.

12:29.550 --> 12:30.870
I need to stay here

12:30.870 --> 12:31.960
with the other candidates.

12:31.960 --> 12:32.960
What did you say?

12:33.960 --> 12:35.000
Well.

12:35.670 --> 12:37.480
Strange as it sounds,

12:38.010 --> 12:39.250
I tested them.

12:39.280 --> 12:41.060
I'm convinced the Shadow Slay League

12:41.060 --> 12:41.990
dare not harm me.

12:45.460 --> 12:46.340
Hold still.

12:47.420 --> 12:49.680
How does that relate to you
staying here?

12:49.710 --> 12:50.920
Think about it.

12:50.940 --> 12:52.340
If my guess holds true,

12:52.710 --> 12:53.870
I can act

12:54.000 --> 12:55.730
as their shield while I remain.

13:00.390 --> 13:01.990
Is that what you intend to do?

13:04.080 --> 13:06.720
We fought hard to launch this
national selection exam,

13:06.720 --> 13:08.780
to gather talent for the Nine Cities.

13:08.910 --> 13:10.420
Among these scholars,

13:10.630 --> 13:11.910
one may emerge

13:12.320 --> 13:14.410
to change the fate of Nine Cities.

13:14.760 --> 13:15.660
So,

13:15.990 --> 13:17.320
I have to stand beside you

13:17.320 --> 13:19.920
and protect these vital pillars
of our cities.

13:20.360 --> 13:21.760
I know you mean to help,

13:22.320 --> 13:23.240
yet this place is far too perilous.

13:23.240 --> 13:24.480
Trust me, Your Excellency.

13:24.480 --> 13:25.840
Don't worry it.

13:25.840 --> 13:26.750
Nothing will go wrong,

13:26.750 --> 13:28.200
I promise.

13:30.670 --> 13:31.720
On one condition.

13:32.380 --> 13:34.190
I will leave Guardian Corps here

13:34.210 --> 13:35.250
to safeguard you.

13:43.240 --> 13:43.870
These texts

13:43.870 --> 13:44.510
are all new to you.

13:44.510 --> 13:46.120
I marked key passages; skim through them quickly to review.
Thank you, Your Excellency.

13:46.120 --> 13:47.510
I've highlighted the key points.

13:47.510 --> 13:49.120
Just do a quick review.

13:49.450 --> 13:50.420
Yes, Teacher.

13:58.050 --> 13:59.580
Second Young Master Zheng.

14:02.630 --> 14:03.510
This must be Tian Yue,

14:03.510 --> 14:05.530
the youngest scholar at Huan'e House

14:05.530 --> 14:07.110
and Fan Yun's pupil.

14:09.640 --> 14:11.240
I shall leave you two to talk.

14:14.870 --> 14:16.180
Judging by your robes—

14:16.440 --> 14:17.560
don't tell me

14:17.580 --> 14:20.150
Second Young Master Zheng plans
to sit the recruitment exam too?

14:20.150 --> 14:20.950
That's right.

14:21.350 --> 14:23.260
Huan'e House gathers like-minded folk,

14:23.260 --> 14:25.790
so I snuck out without my family's knowledge.

14:28.440 --> 14:29.510
But,

14:29.790 --> 14:31.740
this House is far from safe.

14:31.790 --> 14:33.460
Bandits raided here yesterday.

14:33.460 --> 14:34.740
Don't gamble

14:34.920 --> 14:37.320
with your life, Second Young Master Zheng.

14:37.670 --> 14:38.600
When the bandits saw

14:38.600 --> 14:40.150
Lord Zheng's carriage parked out front,

14:40.150 --> 14:41.510
they dare not strike.

14:45.440 --> 14:46.510
You hold such

14:46.550 --> 14:47.960
an exalted status.

14:48.220 --> 14:50.750
Why sudden interest in
the recruitment exam?

14:51.130 --> 14:52.280
I cared nothing for it at first,

14:52.280 --> 14:53.880
but it caught my interest

14:53.910 --> 14:55.100
once you took part.

14:55.720 --> 14:57.290
I care not if I pass or fail;

14:57.340 --> 14:58.670
the journey is all that matters.

14:58.670 --> 14:59.390
Am I right?

15:02.610 --> 15:04.740
You have quite the easygoing mindset.

15:07.830 --> 15:09.690
Even if you can't sit the exam now,

15:09.870 --> 15:11.480
I know you won't give up.

15:11.900 --> 15:13.900
It would be nice to keep you company.

15:15.550 --> 15:17.010
No need to keep me company.

15:17.510 --> 15:20.290
What matters most is you don't add hurdles

15:20.510 --> 15:22.170
for the civilian candidates.

15:27.370 --> 15:28.560
Look what I brought—

15:30.230 --> 15:31.390
pastries,

15:31.410 --> 15:32.200
try some.

15:36.120 --> 15:37.380
Thank you, Second Young Master Zheng.

15:37.380 --> 15:38.130
I'd

15:38.280 --> 15:39.740
rather stick with congee.

15:45.470 --> 15:46.090
I shall

15:46.830 --> 15:48.250
not trouble you further.

15:48.740 --> 15:50.650
I'll share these treats with
the other scholars

15:50.650 --> 15:51.980
to make acquaintances.

16:00.720 --> 16:01.580
Everyone,

16:01.730 --> 16:03.210
I've prepared pastries—

16:03.240 --> 16:04.640
please help yourselves!

16:12.050 --> 16:14.380
-Many thanks! Many thanks!
-Many thanks!

16:15.370 --> 16:16.580
I'm Zheng Shi.

16:16.610 --> 16:17.540
I'm new to this gathering.

16:17.540 --> 16:18.910
It's an honor to study

16:18.940 --> 16:20.000
alongside you all.

16:20.360 --> 16:21.810
My exam result is irrelevant.

16:21.810 --> 16:23.440
Making friends is what it counts to me.

16:23.440 --> 16:24.190
Eat as much as you like,

16:24.190 --> 16:25.120
there's plenty.

16:32.410 --> 16:32.970
What?

16:32.990 --> 16:34.710
Second Young Master Zheng?

16:34.750 --> 16:36.000
It's him?

16:37.000 --> 16:38.270
Don't go, everyone.

16:40.810 --> 16:42.000
It's you.

16:49.150 --> 16:50.080
They all

16:50.080 --> 16:51.740
avoid me as if I'm a wild beast,

16:51.970 --> 16:53.770
all because my surname is Zheng.

17:01.710 --> 17:03.240
Second Young Master Zheng.

17:03.830 --> 17:05.380
The longer

17:06.240 --> 17:07.720
I know you,

17:08.510 --> 17:10.369
the less I seem to understand you.

17:15.240 --> 17:16.750
Your Excellency,

17:16.750 --> 17:18.770
all selection exam papers
have been sealed.

17:18.770 --> 17:21.089
They will be delivered to the examination
compound tomorrow,

17:21.089 --> 17:24.569
and opened the day after.

17:26.400 --> 17:27.250
But...

17:28.550 --> 17:29.480
Speak your mind.

17:29.600 --> 17:31.070
In years past, Lord Zheng

17:31.110 --> 17:33.340
presided over the paper
unsealing ceremony.

17:33.340 --> 17:34.410
But now,

17:35.270 --> 17:37.550
we have no one designated for

17:37.550 --> 17:40.920
the day after tomorrow's rite.

17:48.550 --> 17:50.240
Lord Cai, I assign you

17:51.030 --> 17:52.490
to oversee the unsealing.

17:54.680 --> 17:55.550
Me?

18:00.120 --> 18:01.120
Your Excellency,

18:01.400 --> 18:03.600
that hardly seems proper.

18:03.620 --> 18:05.410
It is His Excellency direct order—

18:05.410 --> 18:06.840
what impropriety is there?

18:06.840 --> 18:07.920
Exactly.

18:10.450 --> 18:11.520
Your Excellency...

18:11.520 --> 18:12.780
Your Excellency,

18:12.810 --> 18:14.890
Lord Zheng requests an audience.

18:17.240 --> 18:18.030
Summon him.

18:37.480 --> 18:38.570
Your Excellency,

18:39.640 --> 18:41.270
I apologize

18:41.640 --> 18:43.430
for my tardiness at this
morning's assembly.

18:43.430 --> 18:46.120
I beg your pardon.

18:46.140 --> 18:47.740
You've arrived just in time.

18:48.480 --> 18:50.080
Lord Cai was consulting me

18:50.680 --> 18:53.720
on who shall preside over this year's
exam paper unsealing.

18:53.720 --> 18:55.070
You've always handled this duty

18:55.070 --> 18:56.370
in prior years.

18:56.880 --> 18:58.640
I feared ill health might keep you

18:58.640 --> 18:59.570
from the burden.

18:59.960 --> 19:01.760
Rest assured, Your Excellency.

19:02.790 --> 19:05.360
As long as I could walk,

19:06.270 --> 19:06.950
I shall

19:07.370 --> 19:08.740
uphold my duties

19:09.920 --> 19:13.030
and never delegate this task to another.

19:16.810 --> 19:17.960
That is ideal.

19:29.110 --> 19:30.550
See how unyielding

19:31.350 --> 19:32.140
Zheng was

19:32.700 --> 19:34.400
in the main hall today?

19:35.770 --> 19:36.680
See?

19:36.790 --> 19:37.480
Zheng

19:37.480 --> 19:38.960
is stubborn as a mule.

19:39.350 --> 19:42.750
What gossip are you two
whispering about me now?

19:45.200 --> 19:47.200
I said he is a stubborn...

19:47.720 --> 19:49.400
I am a stubborn mule.

19:52.000 --> 19:53.200
I said it.

19:53.790 --> 19:54.680
Okay.

19:54.680 --> 19:56.520
I said you are a stubborn mule.

19:58.140 --> 19:59.490
Fine, Zheng.

19:59.520 --> 20:01.440
I'll take tea in place of wine

20:02.000 --> 20:03.270
to apologize to you.

20:07.270 --> 20:08.270
Zheng,

20:08.270 --> 20:09.670
don't stand on ceremony,

20:09.670 --> 20:12.800
refusing this would be rude.

20:14.190 --> 20:14.870
You two...

20:20.210 --> 20:22.130
you two always rely

20:22.960 --> 20:25.550
on this petty goading trick.

20:25.800 --> 20:26.880
Can't you

20:27.310 --> 20:29.400
come up with something new next time?

20:30.270 --> 20:31.720
Fair enough,

20:31.720 --> 20:34.550
we've used this ploy for thirty years.

20:35.880 --> 20:37.060
It's grown stale.

20:37.370 --> 20:38.050
Zhao,

20:38.750 --> 20:40.350
try something new next time.

20:41.160 --> 20:42.550
Alright, alright.

20:43.960 --> 20:45.030
Come.

20:45.030 --> 20:46.070
Tea instead of wine.

20:46.070 --> 20:47.550
Tea instead of wine.

20:49.240 --> 20:49.880
Here.

21:01.370 --> 21:03.360
Have you interrogated the Shadow
Slay League member

21:03.360 --> 21:04.690
we captured yesterday?

21:05.960 --> 21:07.070
He fainted from fright

21:07.070 --> 21:08.400
and hasn't woken up yet.

21:09.300 --> 21:10.630
Have we posted watchers

21:11.030 --> 21:12.230
around Huan'e House?

21:13.310 --> 21:14.480
Gao Ran led the Guardian Corps

21:14.480 --> 21:15.310
to disguise

21:15.310 --> 21:17.200
as street vendors nearby Huan'e House.

21:17.200 --> 21:19.120
They can move instantly at
the slightest trouble.

21:19.120 --> 21:20.920
Guards are stationed at every entrance,

21:20.920 --> 21:21.590
to make sure no one

21:21.590 --> 21:23.450
brings weapon into Huan'e House.

21:27.730 --> 21:29.530
This still isn't secure enough.

21:30.440 --> 21:31.700
I must go there myself.

22:30.740 --> 22:31.740
Get up.

22:31.760 --> 22:32.760
Stop pretending.

22:35.070 --> 22:35.760
Boss.

22:35.920 --> 22:37.400
I knew you'd come save me.

22:39.200 --> 22:40.200
You did?

22:40.730 --> 22:41.490
Of course.

22:41.590 --> 22:42.400
I admire you,

22:42.400 --> 22:43.120
respect you,

22:43.120 --> 22:44.700
and miss you more than anyone.

22:44.700 --> 22:46.310
Then why did you attack her?

22:46.330 --> 22:46.860
I...

22:48.070 --> 22:49.680
I didn't know she was...

22:49.900 --> 22:52.100
It was just a coincidence at the moment.

22:53.450 --> 22:55.190
Should we cut out your tongue

22:58.550 --> 23:00.480
or force needles down your throat?

23:02.790 --> 23:04.470
I'm telling the truth.

23:04.640 --> 23:05.490
I never...

23:05.830 --> 23:07.780
I never meant to hurt her.

23:08.750 --> 23:09.640
I know

23:09.660 --> 23:11.210
she's the one you care for.

23:11.240 --> 23:11.890
Even if

23:11.920 --> 23:13.850
she doesn't return your feelings,

23:13.880 --> 23:15.440
I'd never dare lay a hand on her,

23:15.440 --> 23:16.140
Boss.

23:19.240 --> 23:20.400
What did you say?

23:21.270 --> 23:23.900
Boss, please trust me.

23:24.320 --> 23:25.380
I really... I swear

23:25.400 --> 23:27.600
I had no intention of harming her, Boss.

23:30.830 --> 23:32.750
[Huan'e House]

23:33.220 --> 23:34.850
Ask me anything you want today,

23:34.850 --> 23:36.310
I'll tell you everything.

23:47.720 --> 23:49.450
I grew up in the Zheng household

23:49.890 --> 23:52.620
and never thought fame and wealth
mattered much.

23:53.590 --> 23:55.170
I came to Huan'e House to see

23:55.920 --> 23:57.710
what captivated you, staying up late

23:57.710 --> 23:58.970
to study by lamplight.

24:00.000 --> 24:01.800
It seems I imagined everything.

24:10.550 --> 24:11.440
If everyone

24:12.270 --> 24:13.600
chases fame and profit,

24:14.510 --> 24:16.040
the Nine Cities would fall.

24:18.160 --> 24:19.020
Thankfully,

24:19.440 --> 24:21.160
His Excellency overcame all obstacles

24:21.160 --> 24:23.220
to open the national selection exam.

24:23.400 --> 24:24.330
And now,

24:24.790 --> 24:26.790
common folk can take official posts

24:27.640 --> 24:29.370
and work for the people's good.

24:30.510 --> 24:32.040
You have such noble ideals.

24:36.510 --> 24:37.310
Here,

24:39.350 --> 24:40.280
let me toast you.

24:41.480 --> 24:42.790
I'd rather not.

24:44.070 --> 24:45.400
You and I

24:45.880 --> 24:48.080
can never speak honestly to each other.

24:48.810 --> 24:50.000
So, do drink

24:50.750 --> 24:52.110
without me.

25:03.920 --> 25:05.790
You look troubled.

25:06.650 --> 25:08.370
Did something happen?

25:11.830 --> 25:13.830
I'm surprised you'd worry about me.

25:14.270 --> 25:15.670
Well, I'm wondering why.

25:18.550 --> 25:20.030
There's one thing

25:20.310 --> 25:21.880
I've long wanted to ask you.

25:25.640 --> 25:27.710
Why was Lou Qiyan there

25:27.790 --> 25:29.460
when the Shadow Slay League

25:30.510 --> 25:31.980
tried to attack me?

25:44.770 --> 25:46.330
Whether it's Lou Qiyan

25:47.310 --> 25:48.520
or Zheng Shi,

25:49.670 --> 25:52.200
Shadow Slay League will never
hurt you again.

25:58.450 --> 25:59.690
So

26:00.680 --> 26:01.790
those assassins

26:02.350 --> 26:03.420
work for you?

26:05.950 --> 26:07.550
They are blades in your hand.

26:08.450 --> 26:08.890
You...

26:16.350 --> 26:17.880
Second Young Master Zheng,

26:18.200 --> 26:19.530
I beg you to order them

26:20.110 --> 26:22.040
to leave innocent civilians alone

26:22.400 --> 26:24.400
and never endanger the Nine Cities.

26:24.440 --> 26:26.100
Okay, I promise you.

26:30.270 --> 26:31.270
Fan Yun.

26:40.930 --> 26:42.300
Stay by my side.

26:43.400 --> 26:44.200
Guide me,

26:44.740 --> 26:46.810
let your morals become mine.

26:48.680 --> 26:49.440
I...

26:55.180 --> 26:56.710
Second Young Master Zheng,

26:57.780 --> 26:59.120
I have matters to attend to,

26:59.120 --> 27:00.180
I'll take my leave.

27:36.370 --> 27:37.370
Your Excellency,

27:37.510 --> 27:38.160
bad news.

27:43.360 --> 27:44.360
What did you say?

27:45.030 --> 27:45.960
He's gone mad?

27:46.440 --> 27:47.540
It's absolutely true.

27:47.540 --> 27:49.330
When the Guardian Corps guards
woke to find

27:49.330 --> 27:50.940
the prisoner still locked in the cell,

27:50.940 --> 27:52.550
cackling nonstop,

27:52.580 --> 27:53.440
muttering words

27:53.440 --> 27:54.840
like "sound" and "fool".

27:54.920 --> 27:56.430
The imperial physician found

27:56.430 --> 27:58.210
several needles stuck in his body.

27:58.210 --> 27:59.490
Once removed,

27:59.640 --> 28:01.700
he could no longer speak coherently.

28:02.660 --> 28:04.060
I underestimated my foe.

28:17.760 --> 28:18.950
From today on,

28:19.770 --> 28:22.300
keep a close eye on every move
Zheng Shi makes.

28:33.560 --> 28:35.020
Qi Zheng's carriage.

28:38.260 --> 28:39.100
Hold on!

28:39.240 --> 28:40.030
Wait!

28:42.490 --> 28:43.210
Qi Zheng!

28:43.960 --> 28:44.720
Qi Zheng.

28:45.160 --> 28:46.560
Why did you leave so soon?

28:47.960 --> 28:49.370
You didn't even drop by

28:50.030 --> 28:51.110
and say hello to me.

28:51.110 --> 28:52.770
Do you need something from me?

28:52.920 --> 28:54.300
If not, I have business to attend to.

28:54.300 --> 28:55.150
Wait a minute.

28:56.590 --> 28:57.390
What's wrong?

28:59.550 --> 29:00.590
You

29:00.610 --> 29:01.920
look upset.

29:07.910 --> 29:08.960
Alright then.

29:09.120 --> 29:10.880
If you're in a bad mood,

29:10.900 --> 29:12.350
I won't bother you.

29:12.480 --> 29:13.680
I'll head back first.

29:14.270 --> 29:15.670
Did I say you could leave?

29:18.060 --> 29:19.190
Take a carriage ride

29:19.330 --> 29:20.920
around the town,

29:21.740 --> 29:22.870
then escort Miss Fan

29:23.440 --> 29:24.110
back to Huan'e House.

29:24.110 --> 29:24.720
Go for a ride?

29:24.720 --> 29:26.680
Where are we going for a ride?

29:35.220 --> 29:37.150
Why are we going for another round?

29:46.770 --> 29:47.640
Qi Zheng.

29:48.030 --> 29:49.410
What are you sniffing?

29:50.000 --> 29:52.620
You reek of the scent of men.

29:52.650 --> 29:53.930
Scent of men?

30:00.200 --> 30:01.070
I guess I do.

30:01.070 --> 30:01.680
You...

30:02.400 --> 30:04.480
Then this disguise as a man

30:04.590 --> 30:05.460
will be harder

30:05.830 --> 30:07.470
to see through from now on.

30:07.770 --> 30:09.250
You're teasing me again.

30:10.170 --> 30:10.820
Alright.

30:11.560 --> 30:12.960
I have something for you.

30:17.480 --> 30:18.030
Here.

30:19.380 --> 30:20.380
What is this?

30:20.410 --> 30:22.540
Calming herbal tea to quiet your mind,

30:22.920 --> 30:24.440
so that foul scent won't

30:24.440 --> 30:25.720
keep you awake.

30:26.310 --> 30:28.130
You traveled all this way

30:28.920 --> 30:30.310
just to bring me tea?

30:30.310 --> 30:30.960
Yes.

30:31.880 --> 30:33.680
Yes, I wanted to steady your mind

30:33.790 --> 30:35.650
and stop you from losing control.

30:37.350 --> 30:38.110
Really?

30:46.040 --> 30:47.320
What are you doing?

30:47.340 --> 30:48.000
Don't move.

30:50.510 --> 30:52.180
Let me smell it.

30:52.340 --> 30:53.970
You smell quite nice yourself.

30:53.970 --> 30:56.160
It's just my natural elegant fragrance.

30:56.160 --> 30:57.430
Do you carry a sachet?

30:57.450 --> 30:58.120
No.

30:58.150 --> 30:58.790
You sure?

30:58.790 --> 30:59.160
I'm sure.

30:59.160 --> 31:00.480
-You sure?
-I'm sure.

31:00.480 --> 31:01.240
-You sure?
-I'm sure.

31:01.240 --> 31:02.100
I don't have it.

31:02.310 --> 31:05.040
-Hand it over, or I'll get it myself.
-It tickles!

31:05.970 --> 31:07.380
I knew you had a sachet.

31:07.440 --> 31:08.720
I saw it just now.

31:08.720 --> 31:10.310
You hid it poorly.

31:10.310 --> 31:11.370
This is not for you.

31:14.030 --> 31:15.670
The wish of succeeding
in the imperial exam.

31:15.670 --> 31:17.270
Don't lie, it's meant for me.

31:20.680 --> 31:21.880
It smells wonderful.

31:24.960 --> 31:26.590
It was meant for you.

31:27.750 --> 31:30.000
I specially prayed for this charm for you.

31:30.000 --> 31:31.840
You actually believe in such luck charms?

31:31.840 --> 31:33.080
Of course I do.

31:33.100 --> 31:35.020
I thought you'd sit the exam,

31:35.160 --> 31:36.270
and I was so anxious

31:37.310 --> 31:39.160
I went to pray for your

31:39.180 --> 31:40.290
smooth progress.

31:43.240 --> 31:44.750
You shouldn't believe these things.

31:44.750 --> 31:45.920
Give it back to me.

31:47.080 --> 31:48.660
Since you prayed for it for me,

31:48.660 --> 31:49.820
it's mine now.

31:50.070 --> 31:50.750
Thank you.

31:52.880 --> 31:55.210
I was afraid it would make you sad
to see it.

31:58.110 --> 31:59.000
Well,

31:59.640 --> 32:00.850
let the past

32:00.960 --> 32:01.920
be the past.

32:02.680 --> 32:04.160
We have to move on anyway.

32:05.320 --> 32:06.920
This is your heartfelt gift.

32:07.590 --> 32:08.790
I will cherish it.

32:12.030 --> 32:13.760
We've arrived at Huan'e House.

32:32.310 --> 32:33.840
-What?
-I thought about it.

32:34.310 --> 32:35.150
That sachet,

32:35.470 --> 32:36.970
I only lent it to you temporarily.

32:36.970 --> 32:38.570
Remember to return it later.

32:38.930 --> 32:40.020
Fine, fine.

32:40.200 --> 32:41.880
You're so petty.

32:56.170 --> 32:56.690
Go.

32:59.510 --> 32:59.940
I...

32:59.960 --> 33:00.480
I'm...

33:02.280 --> 33:02.940
I'm off now.

33:17.920 --> 33:20.510
Your Excellency, you summoned me, a plain
commoner to this remote wilderness.

33:20.510 --> 33:21.970
Is there an urgent matter?

33:22.880 --> 33:23.880
A plain commoner?

33:27.310 --> 33:29.250
You really know how to humble yourself.

33:29.250 --> 33:32.350
You control both the Juyun Pavilion
and Shadow Slay League.

33:32.350 --> 33:33.930
No one else across the Nine Cities

33:33.930 --> 33:36.660
wields such power, except you,
a plain commoner.

33:43.920 --> 33:45.460
I don't know what Your Excellency implies.

33:45.460 --> 33:47.390
But Fan Yun told me

33:47.950 --> 33:50.830
she would never draw her blade
against innocent civilians,

33:50.830 --> 33:51.790
and I share

33:52.240 --> 33:53.500
her view.

33:57.650 --> 34:00.050
You are Lord Zheng's most valued grandson.

34:00.820 --> 34:02.220
You'd be a valuable asset

34:03.090 --> 34:04.370
if you serve me,

34:04.930 --> 34:06.610
and I would welcome it.

34:08.150 --> 34:09.600
Yet I hate

34:09.900 --> 34:11.900
forcing others against their will.

34:13.030 --> 34:14.590
You may have your own ways

34:15.000 --> 34:16.920
to feed and enrich the people

34:17.239 --> 34:18.560
of the Nine Cities,

34:19.400 --> 34:20.620
yet those methods

34:21.130 --> 34:22.659
may bring ruin to our realm.

34:23.650 --> 34:25.810
As Governor, I must warn you:

34:26.570 --> 34:28.920
any act harming the Nine Cities

34:29.850 --> 34:32.179
will be fully investigated and punished.

34:32.260 --> 34:33.489
When that time comes,

34:33.520 --> 34:35.400
if you

34:35.420 --> 34:36.540
or the Zheng clan

34:37.300 --> 34:38.190
are involved,

34:39.469 --> 34:40.909
there will be no mercy.

35:16.740 --> 35:19.390
♪ Our hearts reach for the morning glow ♪

35:19.560 --> 35:23.020
♪ Our dreams fear no barren land below ♪

35:23.670 --> 35:28.760
♪ What matter if we fly against the wind ♪

35:29.200 --> 35:31.780
♪ We vow to live up to
our youthful prime ♪

35:32.040 --> 35:35.850
♪ To walk alongside ordinary folks alike ♪

35:36.420 --> 35:39.350
♪ Sharing the same ray of light ♪

35:39.520 --> 35:45.060
♪ Fear no strange land nor dim twilight ♪

35:45.230 --> 35:48.300
♪ All for this boundless world ♪

35:48.320 --> 35:53.430
♪ To wear a robe of radiant glory ♪

35:54.840 --> 36:00.420
♪ Face the light, gaze ahead
with brave eyes ♪

36:00.610 --> 36:04.800
♪ Let all darkness and hurt step aside ♪

36:04.830 --> 36:06.960
♪ It's unstoppable ♪

36:07.160 --> 36:12.850
♪ Chase the light, let our
dreams unfold wide ♪

36:12.970 --> 36:17.200
♪ With bold resolve, ignite plain faith ♪

36:17.220 --> 36:19.090
♪ Light them up ♪

36:19.110 --> 36:22.840
♪ Let all wind and frost of days gone by ♪

36:22.980 --> 36:29.060
♪ Turn to countless beams of light
within my eye ♪

36:29.080 --> 36:35.340
♪ Await the sight of you ♪

36:52.410 --> 36:53.770
Dressed so shabbily,

36:53.800 --> 36:55.590
you dare take the same exam venue as us?

36:55.590 --> 36:56.730
How shameless.

36:57.440 --> 36:58.730
What's worse,

36:58.760 --> 37:00.280
there's even a child here.

37:04.010 --> 37:06.210
It seems they see me as
some strange curiosity.

37:06.210 --> 37:07.790
As long as you don't think
poorly of yourself,

37:07.790 --> 37:09.670
others' words can never hurt you.

37:19.550 --> 37:20.430
Lord Yan.

37:23.110 --> 37:23.920
Lord Yan.

37:23.940 --> 37:24.540
Wei Rong,

37:25.770 --> 37:26.990
your brother even bet with me,

37:26.990 --> 37:28.450
saying you wouldn't come.

37:28.850 --> 37:30.580
He never truly understands me.

37:31.990 --> 37:33.320
As expected of Wei Rong.

37:39.390 --> 37:40.570
So you are Wei Rong.

37:40.970 --> 37:43.230
What is your relationship with Lord Yan?

37:48.390 --> 37:50.720
How could Lord Yan befriend an eccentric?

37:52.710 --> 37:54.000
Lord Yan is a knowledgeable man.

37:54.000 --> 37:55.400
He must have his reasons.

39:56.920 --> 39:57.920
Your Excellency.

40:00.230 --> 40:01.310
Why are you here?

40:01.920 --> 40:02.840
Weren't you

40:03.130 --> 40:05.150
supposed to be at the examination academy?

40:05.150 --> 40:07.210
In the academy, there are examiners.

40:07.770 --> 40:08.750
But you

40:09.440 --> 40:11.240
have no one to talk to beside you.

40:12.300 --> 40:13.560
I thought you needed me

40:15.360 --> 40:16.460
more than

40:16.720 --> 40:18.460
the academy today.

40:21.600 --> 40:22.810
Everyone has

40:22.830 --> 40:25.490
stayed up late studying day
and night recently.

40:26.120 --> 40:27.130
I hope

40:27.880 --> 40:29.610
they all achieve good results.

40:32.680 --> 40:33.600
What about you?

40:35.230 --> 40:36.500
You worked just as hard

40:37.240 --> 40:38.990
yet cannot sit the exam.

40:39.930 --> 40:41.130
Doesn't it upset you?

40:42.910 --> 40:44.850
I've told you many times.

40:45.550 --> 40:46.960
I'm long past being sad.

40:49.480 --> 40:50.440
Good.

40:51.320 --> 40:53.450
I know you hate admitting you're hurt.

40:53.870 --> 40:56.530
I even traveled all the way to the Bureau
of Sacred Rites

40:56.530 --> 40:57.590
to sort things out.

40:57.880 --> 40:59.030
What do you mean?

41:00.400 --> 41:02.840
Even though you can't sit
for the exam to become

41:02.840 --> 41:03.920
an official this time,

41:03.920 --> 41:05.150
there is still a way.

41:08.230 --> 41:09.220
Your Excellency.

41:09.220 --> 41:10.770
Your Excellency, you find a way

41:10.770 --> 41:12.420
without waiting until next year?
